1
00:01:30,800 --> 00:01:34,520
=Lady Liberty=

2
00:01:35,020 --> 00:01:37,940
=Episode 3=

3
00:01:55,933 --> 00:01:57,060
What do you want to eat?

4
00:01:58,340 --> 00:01:59,300
You.

5
00:02:00,580 --> 00:02:01,820
Too greasy. I don't eat that.

6
00:02:01,940 --> 00:02:02,755
Let's have porridge.

7
00:02:08,660 --> 00:02:10,100
Why did you wipe it off?

8
00:02:10,420 --> 00:02:11,380
Allergy. It's itchy.

9
00:02:12,311 --> 00:02:13,733
Then, I'll draw another one for you.

10
00:02:14,500 --> 00:02:15,180
No...

11
00:02:15,580 --> 00:02:16,820
It'll affect driving safety.

12
00:02:29,620 --> 00:02:30,780
Is what He Han said true?

13
00:02:32,020 --> 00:02:32,420
Yes.

14
00:02:32,777 --> 00:02:34,444
When were you planning to tell me?

15
00:02:34,740 --> 00:02:35,460
In a week

16
00:02:35,900 --> 00:02:36,580
or a month.

17
00:02:36,955 --> 00:02:38,940
When you're ready,
either you leave, or I leave.

18
00:02:38,940 --> 00:02:39,580
Why?

19
00:02:40,220 --> 00:02:41,780
Is there a problem at work?

20
00:02:49,620 --> 00:02:50,180
Marry me.

21
00:02:51,955 --> 00:02:53,800
This is the second time
I'm proposing to you.

22
00:02:53,940 --> 00:02:55,200
Well, this is my second answer.

23
00:02:55,420 --> 00:02:57,100
Dating and marriage are not my thing.

24
00:02:57,940 --> 00:02:58,780
If you say yes,

25
00:02:59,900 --> 00:03:00,820
I'll dump Zhao Lanxin.

26
00:03:01,700 --> 00:03:02,820
We can run Chenxing together.

27
00:03:03,133 --> 00:03:04,460
Otherwise, I really don't have

28
00:03:04,580 --> 00:03:05,888
a reason to stay and help you.

29
00:03:06,000 --> 00:03:07,733
Our share percentages
are almost the same.

30
00:03:07,740 --> 00:03:09,577
When we make money,
you don't get less than I do.

31
00:03:09,600 --> 00:03:10,933
How did it become you helping me?

32
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:12,600
I'm helping you
get out of He Han's shadow.

33
00:03:12,644 --> 00:03:13,820
I don't see any shadow,

34
00:03:13,911 --> 00:03:15,822
and I don't need you
to help me get out of one.

35
00:03:15,980 --> 00:03:16,820
If there is a shadow,

36
00:03:17,060 --> 00:03:18,460
it's in your own heart.

37
00:03:18,620 --> 00:03:19,500
You can act tough,

38
00:03:19,500 --> 00:03:20,540
but everyone saw

39
00:03:20,540 --> 00:03:21,688
He Han's attitude toward you.

40
00:03:22,580 --> 00:03:24,420
I admit he's a genius in some ways,

41
00:03:24,540 --> 00:03:26,511
but that doesn't change
the fact that he's a jerk.

42
00:03:26,733 --> 00:03:27,780
Do you really want to keep

43
00:03:27,780 --> 00:03:29,755
thinking about him
every day at work and after work?

44
00:03:29,822 --> 00:03:30,577
There's no need.

45
00:03:31,660 --> 00:03:32,140
I don't.

46
00:03:32,460 --> 00:03:34,620
Every day, you shout
that you want to take down He Han.

47
00:03:34,620 --> 00:03:36,577
Does that mean you're invincible
and untouchable?

48
00:03:36,666 --> 00:03:38,622
The more you act like this,
the more it proves

49
00:03:38,630 --> 00:03:39,820
you simply can't get past

50
00:03:39,820 --> 00:03:41,220
the hurdle He Han left you with.

51
00:03:48,355 --> 00:03:49,911
Since He Han is important to me,

52
00:03:49,977 --> 00:03:51,090
I was not afraid when he left.

53
00:03:51,100 --> 00:03:51,733
If you leave,

54
00:03:52,740 --> 00:03:53,540
I care even less.

55
00:04:31,660 --> 00:04:32,500
Hello, Lawyer Zhang,

56
00:04:32,577 --> 00:04:34,460
could you please
help me contact Lawyer Bei?

57
00:04:34,470 --> 00:04:36,050
I have something urgent
to discuss with him.

58
00:04:36,088 --> 00:04:36,977
He's in a meeting?

59
00:04:37,660 --> 00:04:38,060
Then,

60
00:04:38,540 --> 00:04:40,060
can I come by at noon to see him?

61
00:04:42,911 --> 00:04:44,200
Okay, thank you.

62
00:04:53,180 --> 00:04:53,780
Hello, Mei.

63
00:04:53,977 --> 00:04:55,555
Something happened at my company.

64
00:04:55,644 --> 00:04:57,230
Help me set up
a meeting with Lawyer Bei.

65
00:04:58,380 --> 00:04:58,860
Go ahead.

66
00:05:06,020 --> 00:05:06,980
Okay, no problem.

67
00:05:29,020 --> 00:05:29,500
Zhanqiao,

68
00:05:30,060 --> 00:05:30,460
hello.

69
00:05:30,800 --> 00:05:32,980
Sorry, Mr. Bei, for asking you out
on such short notice.

70
00:05:33,180 --> 00:05:33,580
Sit.

71
00:05:38,288 --> 00:05:39,260
Mei has already told me

72
00:05:39,420 --> 00:05:40,660
about your situation.

73
00:05:41,260 --> 00:05:42,620
It's not a very complicated issue.

74
00:05:42,780 --> 00:05:44,260
You all eat in peace

75
00:05:44,555 --> 00:05:45,940
and then go to work as usual.

76
00:05:46,300 --> 00:05:47,380
As for Hong Qigong,

77
00:05:47,460 --> 00:05:49,444
I've already asked
Zhang Yousen to go there.

78
00:05:50,380 --> 00:05:52,300
He's the Lawyer Zhang
who answered your call.

79
00:05:52,820 --> 00:05:54,540
He's my student and also my assistant.

80
00:05:56,140 --> 00:05:57,660
The story idea and concept

81
00:05:58,180 --> 00:05:59,420
have not yet been written down,

82
00:05:59,533 --> 00:06:02,050
so they were all discussed
verbally between Hong Qigong,

83
00:06:02,088 --> 00:06:04,355
the editorial assistant,
and me during planning meetings.

84
00:06:04,622 --> 00:06:06,777
Now, if Hong Qigong
wants to leave, that's fine,

85
00:06:06,860 --> 00:06:08,020
but this thing isn't hers.

86
00:06:08,422 --> 00:06:09,866
She can't take it with her.

87
00:06:10,060 --> 00:06:11,820
You must have meeting records,

88
00:06:11,900 --> 00:06:13,260
or recordings, or something, right?

89
00:06:13,860 --> 00:06:15,900
If you do, give them to Zhang Yousen.

90
00:06:16,060 --> 00:06:17,300
After he meets Hong Qigong,

91
00:06:17,460 --> 00:06:18,740
he'll report back to me.

92
00:06:19,100 --> 00:06:20,220
If there are any issues,

93
00:06:20,300 --> 00:06:21,260
I'll follow up in time.

94
00:06:25,860 --> 00:06:27,420
I still have a client waiting upstairs.

95
00:06:27,620 --> 00:06:29,060
Take your time eating. I'll go first.

96
00:06:29,940 --> 00:06:30,770
Thank you.

97
00:06:30,770 --> 00:06:31,180
Alright.

98
00:06:33,220 --> 00:06:34,500
The firm will cover this bill.

99
00:06:35,333 --> 00:06:37,230
You don't need to worry
after you finish eating.

100
00:06:40,860 --> 00:06:41,300
Goodbye.

101
00:06:47,222 --> 00:06:48,820
How did you manage to get him here?

102
00:06:49,700 --> 00:06:50,700
His assistant said

103
00:06:50,700 --> 00:06:51,820
he was busy in a meeting.

104
00:06:51,955 --> 00:06:54,133
Even if someone is busy,
it depends on who it's for.

105
00:06:54,177 --> 00:06:56,333
For some people, they don't
even have time to look at you.

106
00:06:56,340 --> 00:06:58,490
For others, they'll fly around
the world for three days

107
00:06:58,500 --> 00:07:00,355
and still report to you
morning and night.

108
00:07:00,720 --> 00:07:02,066
What's your relationship with him?

109
00:07:02,260 --> 00:07:03,540
My company is his client.

110
00:07:04,700 --> 00:07:06,300
He has a wife and kids, you know?

111
00:07:06,580 --> 00:07:07,180
I know.

112
00:07:07,777 --> 00:07:08,980
Just because he has a family,

113
00:07:09,220 --> 00:07:10,380
does that mean we can't talk?

114
00:07:12,340 --> 00:07:14,100
I can tell exactly what you're thinking.

115
00:07:14,555 --> 00:07:16,333
Don't make the same mistake again.

116
00:07:17,180 --> 00:07:18,940
I wouldn't dare cross the line.

117
00:07:20,660 --> 00:07:21,460
He likes you?

118
00:07:21,860 --> 00:07:23,420
There are plenty of men who like me.

119
00:07:23,533 --> 00:07:25,022
So, it means you're leading him on.

120
00:07:25,180 --> 00:07:26,020
You...

121
00:07:26,133 --> 00:07:28,688
Just because I'm good-looking,
that means I'm leading him on?

122
00:07:28,820 --> 00:07:29,980
You asked me to set this up.

123
00:07:29,980 --> 00:07:30,820
I got him here for you,

124
00:07:30,820 --> 00:07:31,820
and now you're nitpicking.

125
00:07:31,820 --> 00:07:32,911
What's wrong with you?

126
00:07:33,420 --> 00:07:34,700
I'm reminding you.

127
00:07:35,088 --> 00:07:37,600
If there's a problem, fix it.
If not, stay alert.

128
00:07:39,740 --> 00:07:40,220
Hello.

129
00:07:41,555 --> 00:07:42,733
I won't stay for the meal.

130
00:07:42,844 --> 00:07:45,222
I'll come find you tonight
to follow up on the progress.

131
00:07:45,380 --> 00:07:46,644
You're in such a hurry?

132
00:07:46,777 --> 00:07:48,533
Li Weifeng's wife will come to see me.

133
00:07:50,820 --> 00:07:52,180
You should be careful, then.

134
00:07:52,860 --> 00:07:54,140
How about I go with you?

135
00:07:54,540 --> 00:07:54,940
It's fine.

136
00:07:55,820 --> 00:07:57,420
I'm going to save her marriage.

137
00:07:57,700 --> 00:07:58,900
She should be thanking me.

138
00:07:59,020 --> 00:08:00,060
With the face of yours,

139
00:08:00,380 --> 00:08:02,044
you can't save anyone's marriage.

140
00:08:02,460 --> 00:08:04,466
It's already good enough
if you don't ruin it.

141
00:08:05,020 --> 00:08:06,100
Don't make things worse.

142
00:08:09,460 --> 00:08:11,500
I dislike and pity

143
00:08:12,020 --> 00:08:13,740
a woman like Li Weifeng's wife.

144
00:08:15,820 --> 00:08:16,900
She reminds me of my mother.

145
00:08:47,340 --> 00:08:48,220
Hello, Lawyer Zhang.

146
00:08:49,200 --> 00:08:50,644
You went to see Hong Qigong?

147
00:08:51,820 --> 00:08:52,180
Get lost!

148
00:08:53,060 --> 00:08:53,850
Ms. Hong.

149
00:08:53,850 --> 00:08:55,380
Ms. Hong, wait! Please, Ms. Hong.

150
00:08:58,260 --> 00:08:58,980
Ms. Hong.

151
00:08:59,060 --> 00:09:00,540
You've misunderstood me, Ms. Hong.

152
00:09:06,020 --> 00:09:06,780
Ms. Hong.

153
00:09:17,540 --> 00:09:18,380
Ms. Hong?

154
00:09:22,740 --> 00:09:23,740
Ms. Hong Qigong.

155
00:09:24,460 --> 00:09:25,460
Lin.

156
00:09:27,620 --> 00:09:29,460
Editor-in-Chief Lin,

157
00:09:30,700 --> 00:09:32,340
you've disappointed me.

158
00:09:33,380 --> 00:09:35,060
You've hurt me, you know?

159
00:09:35,860 --> 00:09:37,020
I'm sorry, Ms. Hong.

160
00:09:37,020 --> 00:09:38,860
You sent such a young lawyer

161
00:09:38,860 --> 00:09:39,900
to talk to me about this.

162
00:09:41,420 --> 00:09:42,820
You're looking down on me.

163
00:09:44,500 --> 00:09:46,540
Who told you I wasn't renewing with you?

164
00:09:47,180 --> 00:09:48,660
Even if someone told you,

165
00:09:48,780 --> 00:09:50,820
shouldn't you have come to ask me first?

166
00:09:51,300 --> 00:09:53,460
Who is it that you choose to believe,

167
00:09:53,860 --> 00:09:55,020
or is it that you

168
00:09:55,020 --> 00:09:57,780
do not even trust me at all?

169
00:09:58,180 --> 00:09:59,180
I was wrong.

170
00:09:59,288 --> 00:10:00,300
I believed too easily.

171
00:10:00,300 --> 00:10:00,900
Ms. Hong.

172
00:10:01,980 --> 00:10:02,780
Coming.

173
00:10:02,955 --> 00:10:03,900
Are you here, Ms. Hong?

174
00:10:03,900 --> 00:10:05,300
Coming.

175
00:10:07,580 --> 00:10:08,740
Mr. Chen, right?

176
00:10:09,420 --> 00:10:10,660
Come, I'm upstairs.

177
00:10:10,680 --> 00:10:11,740
I'll come down and get you.

178
00:10:11,740 --> 00:10:13,244
This place is a bit hard to find, huh?

179
00:10:13,288 --> 00:10:14,355
Watch your step.

180
00:10:14,540 --> 00:10:15,900
The stairway is a bit narrow.

181
00:10:15,977 --> 00:10:16,930
You're upstairs, right?

182
00:10:16,930 --> 00:10:17,620
Coming.

183
00:10:20,311 --> 00:10:21,580
- Ms. Hong.
- Mr. Chen, right?

184
00:10:21,800 --> 00:10:23,620
I've already prepared
everything for you.

185
00:10:23,620 --> 00:10:23,980
Right?

186
00:10:25,100 --> 00:10:25,660
Come.

187
00:10:25,844 --> 00:10:27,540
- We've been waiting for you.
- Alright.

188
00:10:27,900 --> 00:10:29,180
Hu sent me.

189
00:10:30,940 --> 00:10:32,140
A friend of Hu

190
00:10:32,300 --> 00:10:33,860
is a friend of mine.

191
00:10:34,860 --> 00:10:35,780
Come, come.

192
00:10:36,300 --> 00:10:38,380
Everything's ready for you.

193
00:10:38,980 --> 00:10:39,580
It's this one.

194
00:10:40,020 --> 00:10:40,580
Take a look.

195
00:10:40,940 --> 00:10:41,555
Alright.

196
00:10:42,620 --> 00:10:43,940
Let me pour you some tea.

197
00:10:44,740 --> 00:10:45,980
The price is negotiable.

198
00:10:46,380 --> 00:10:47,260
Okay, thank you.

199
00:10:47,420 --> 00:10:48,660
Here, have some tea.

200
00:10:49,940 --> 00:10:50,460
Good tea.

201
00:10:51,460 --> 00:10:53,940
This should be top-grade Laobanzhang.

202
00:10:55,244 --> 00:10:55,700
Thank you.

203
00:10:55,700 --> 00:10:56,340
Take your time.

204
00:10:56,660 --> 00:10:57,140
Alright.

205
00:11:04,340 --> 00:11:07,260
My novels are written for young readers,

206
00:11:07,780 --> 00:11:10,340
but I'm an old-school woman.

207
00:11:11,260 --> 00:11:12,540
Trust, you know?

208
00:11:13,060 --> 00:11:16,420
Trust is the foundation
of long-term cooperation.

209
00:11:16,900 --> 00:11:19,180
You're one of
the top editors in the industry.

210
00:11:19,380 --> 00:11:20,780
Your track record speaks for itself.

211
00:11:21,660 --> 00:11:22,180
As for me,

212
00:11:22,820 --> 00:11:24,980
I'm not some newcomer either, alright?

213
00:11:25,900 --> 00:11:27,940
Those story proposals
you are worried about...

214
00:11:28,260 --> 00:11:29,980
I will not touch what is yours.

215
00:11:30,940 --> 00:11:31,420
Ms. Hong,

216
00:11:31,488 --> 00:11:33,377
can I take a look
at your other materials?

217
00:11:33,380 --> 00:11:34,620
Go ahead.

218
00:11:34,860 --> 00:11:35,970
Everything's negotiable.

219
00:11:35,970 --> 00:11:36,460
Alright.

220
00:11:37,500 --> 00:11:39,180
Since I've said this much,

221
00:11:39,660 --> 00:11:41,260
I'll be even more direct.

222
00:11:42,700 --> 00:11:44,380
If you think

223
00:11:44,380 --> 00:11:46,260
I can't beat He Han on the rankings,

224
00:11:46,333 --> 00:11:48,200
and that's why
you're putting on this act,

225
00:11:48,300 --> 00:11:50,220
then there's no need
to beat around the bush.

226
00:11:51,220 --> 00:11:52,860
Whoever you think can beat him,

227
00:11:53,140 --> 00:11:54,940
just let them do it.

228
00:11:55,540 --> 00:11:55,980
Alright?

229
00:11:56,420 --> 00:11:57,060
That's it.

230
00:11:57,222 --> 00:11:58,422
I have business to attend to.

231
00:11:58,460 --> 00:11:59,244
Please leave.

232
00:11:59,820 --> 00:12:00,580
Come on.

233
00:12:21,133 --> 00:12:22,530
Hello, Sir. Everything's ready.

234
00:12:22,540 --> 00:12:23,300
Here, thank you.

235
00:12:23,377 --> 00:12:24,622
Alright, thank you, Sir.

236
00:12:31,088 --> 00:12:32,580
Where are you? I'm outside your room.

237
00:12:32,733 --> 00:12:33,688
I need to talk to you.

238
00:12:33,755 --> 00:12:34,460
I'm not there.

239
00:12:34,460 --> 00:12:35,180
Didn't I tell you

240
00:12:35,180 --> 00:12:36,620
I moved across from your company?

241
00:13:02,500 --> 00:13:03,140
Lin Zhanqiao.

242
00:13:04,288 --> 00:13:05,044
I'm Dai Shan.

243
00:13:05,420 --> 00:13:05,780
Hello.

244
00:13:06,900 --> 00:13:08,220
The first time I heard about you

245
00:13:08,220 --> 00:13:10,500
was when you left the publishing house.

246
00:13:10,644 --> 00:13:12,288
I submitted my resume to you before.

247
00:13:12,377 --> 00:13:13,288
You didn't hire me.

248
00:13:14,220 --> 00:13:16,780
For someone this pretty,
I wouldn't dare.

249
00:13:17,900 --> 00:13:19,300
That's judging by appearance.

250
00:13:20,466 --> 00:13:22,210
He Han is at the cafe
on the second floor,

251
00:13:22,220 --> 00:13:23,940
meeting with platform executives.

252
00:13:24,355 --> 00:13:26,222
If you go up,
you might have to wait a bit.

253
00:13:26,380 --> 00:13:26,900
No problem.

254
00:13:33,420 --> 00:13:34,500
You can wait here for now.

255
00:14:25,400 --> 00:14:26,860
- Come, I'll walk you out.
- Come.

256
00:14:26,860 --> 00:14:27,780
- Thank you.
- Alright.

257
00:14:29,380 --> 00:14:30,260
Ms. Lin, you're here.

258
00:14:30,420 --> 00:14:31,300
Come, have a seat.

259
00:14:31,860 --> 00:14:32,780
Another black coffee.

260
00:14:32,860 --> 00:14:33,660
Skim milk, no sugar.

261
00:14:33,900 --> 00:14:34,580
How did you know

262
00:14:34,580 --> 00:14:36,150
Hong Qigong was going
to sign with Zhao Lanxin?

263
00:14:36,180 --> 00:14:36,700
Just a guess.

264
00:14:37,100 --> 00:14:38,088
What, did you go see her?

265
00:14:38,180 --> 00:14:39,155
So she didn't sign?

266
00:14:39,340 --> 00:14:41,620
Good. Then keep working
with her and compete with me.

267
00:14:41,620 --> 00:14:43,422
Can you stop
pushing me to call you a jerk?

268
00:14:43,620 --> 00:14:44,420
You already did.

269
00:14:44,622 --> 00:14:46,200
You're not welcome at my company.

270
00:14:46,266 --> 00:14:47,340
Don't show up again.

271
00:14:47,420 --> 00:14:49,066
Your company is about to fall apart.

272
00:14:50,020 --> 00:14:51,180
Fine, I won't come to you.

273
00:14:51,311 --> 00:14:52,400
You don't come to me either.

274
00:14:52,460 --> 00:14:54,150
From now on, we stay out
of each other's business!

275
00:14:54,180 --> 00:14:55,460
If you have what it takes,
keep your number one spot.

276
00:14:55,460 --> 00:14:57,400
If I have what it takes,
my authors will surpass you.

277
00:14:57,420 --> 00:14:58,630
From now on, we let our work speak!

278
00:14:58,644 --> 00:14:59,733
No contact or interaction!

279
00:14:59,940 --> 00:15:00,800
Lin Zhanqiao, you can't

280
00:15:00,822 --> 00:15:02,860
even write better than I do,
and you're teaching others?

281
00:15:02,860 --> 00:15:04,060
Doesn't that make it even worse?

282
00:15:04,070 --> 00:15:05,330
Such a simple truth.
You don't get it?

283
00:15:05,340 --> 00:15:07,300
A good editor with a good author

284
00:15:07,300 --> 00:15:08,620
is one plus one greater than two.

285
00:15:08,688 --> 00:15:11,155
A great author alone
is already worth many times more.

286
00:15:11,900 --> 00:15:12,540
One day,

287
00:15:12,540 --> 00:15:13,900
you'll pay for your arrogance!

288
00:15:14,060 --> 00:15:15,380
Enjoy it while it lasts.

289
00:15:15,488 --> 00:15:16,888
The view from my room is amazing.

290
00:15:16,911 --> 00:15:17,860
Want to take a look?

291
00:15:17,860 --> 00:15:18,490
Not interested.

292
00:15:18,500 --> 00:15:19,140
Next time, then.

293
00:15:19,300 --> 00:15:20,300
We're so close anyway.

294
00:15:20,580 --> 00:15:21,800
Drop by when you have time.

295
00:15:30,644 --> 00:15:32,622
These were all given
to me by your husband.

296
00:15:32,640 --> 00:15:34,111
I'm returning everything to you today.

297
00:15:37,488 --> 00:15:38,580
This is what he sent me.

298
00:15:39,700 --> 00:15:40,660
As long as I agreed,

299
00:15:40,660 --> 00:15:42,311
he said he could
divorce you immediately.

300
00:15:42,940 --> 00:15:44,060
(Li Weifeng: You
received the bag, right?)

301
00:15:44,066 --> 00:15:44,700
(She has no taste.)

302
00:15:44,700 --> 00:15:45,860
(Only when I talk to you
do I feel a real connection.)

303
00:15:45,860 --> 00:15:47,060
(Zhou Mei: Your wife
misunderstood me before.)

304
00:15:47,060 --> 00:15:48,977
(Li Weifeng: You look
stunning today. I'm captivated.)

305
00:15:49,000 --> 00:15:49,820
(I truly like you.)

306
00:15:51,555 --> 00:15:53,022
You can keep deleting them.

307
00:15:59,155 --> 00:16:01,244
And you still say you
didn't seduce my husband?

308
00:16:01,355 --> 00:16:02,266
Before, I didn't.

309
00:16:02,900 --> 00:16:03,500
Now, I did.

310
00:16:05,580 --> 00:16:07,050
I just wanted to show you

311
00:16:07,050 --> 00:16:07,940
that if I wanted to,

312
00:16:08,088 --> 00:16:09,420
getting him to spend money on me

313
00:16:09,420 --> 00:16:10,300
or even divorce for me

314
00:16:10,300 --> 00:16:11,820
wouldn't be difficult at all.

315
00:16:12,822 --> 00:16:14,422
On the contrary, his obsession with love

316
00:16:14,488 --> 00:16:15,740
isn't something you can fix

317
00:16:15,740 --> 00:16:18,088
just by reporting me
and deleting our chat history.

318
00:16:19,340 --> 00:16:20,140
What do you want?

319
00:16:22,422 --> 00:16:24,260
What I can do
is stay away from your husband.

320
00:16:25,400 --> 00:16:27,222
But I'm not the one
you should be watching.

321
00:16:27,260 --> 00:16:28,620
You should be thanking me.

322
00:16:29,140 --> 00:16:30,140
With how eager he is,

323
00:16:30,200 --> 00:16:32,222
I've never once been interested in him.

324
00:16:37,100 --> 00:16:38,580
You can pay for this coffee today.

325
00:16:38,911 --> 00:16:40,755
I just saved your family a lot of money.

326
00:17:06,620 --> 00:17:07,260
Ms. Lin?

327
00:17:08,220 --> 00:17:08,620
Hello.

328
00:17:08,711 --> 00:17:11,022
I'm Zhang Yousen,
Assistant Lawyer to Lawyer Bei.

329
00:17:11,180 --> 00:17:11,780
Hello.

330
00:17:11,822 --> 00:17:13,866
Sorry about earlier.
It was a misunderstanding.

331
00:17:14,311 --> 00:17:15,780
I've already reported to Lawyer Bei.

332
00:17:15,940 --> 00:17:16,900
He asked me to follow up

333
00:17:16,900 --> 00:17:18,977
on the issue of
your executive leaving the company.

334
00:17:19,111 --> 00:17:20,180
Please thank him for me.

335
00:17:20,180 --> 00:17:21,422
He's been very thoughtful.

336
00:17:21,940 --> 00:17:22,860
If you don't mind,

337
00:17:22,870 --> 00:17:24,000
shall we go upstairs and talk?

338
00:17:24,380 --> 00:17:24,700
Sure.

339
00:17:31,620 --> 00:17:32,140
Ms. Lin,

340
00:17:32,244 --> 00:17:34,560
I have a general understanding
of your company's situation.

341
00:17:34,666 --> 00:17:35,580
Could you tell me more

342
00:17:35,580 --> 00:17:38,111
about your working relationship
with Ling Yikai and Zhao Lanxin?

343
00:17:39,660 --> 00:17:41,140
Ling Yikai is the Finance Director.

344
00:17:41,460 --> 00:17:42,940
Zhao Lanxin is a Senior Editor.

345
00:17:43,355 --> 00:17:45,733
The three of us
are partners in the company.

346
00:17:46,060 --> 00:17:47,140
I don't know why

347
00:17:47,140 --> 00:17:48,777
they suddenly brought up resigning.

348
00:17:49,100 --> 00:17:50,460
But since it's already happened,

349
00:17:50,900 --> 00:17:51,700
I'll accept it.

350
00:17:51,888 --> 00:17:53,220
What I care about are my authors

351
00:17:53,340 --> 00:17:55,066
and the projects currently in progress.

352
00:17:55,070 --> 00:17:56,050
If my authors stay, I stay.

353
00:17:56,050 --> 00:17:57,622
Any other difficulties, I can handle.

354
00:18:01,200 --> 00:18:02,000
Thank you.

355
00:18:04,180 --> 00:18:04,740
Have a seat.

356
00:18:09,460 --> 00:18:10,460
First,

357
00:18:10,700 --> 00:18:12,020
how to explain this externally?

358
00:18:12,820 --> 00:18:14,940
Second, how to divide the interests?

359
00:18:15,780 --> 00:18:17,340
Third, how will the company continue?

360
00:18:17,980 --> 00:18:18,577
Thank you.

361
00:18:19,340 --> 00:18:20,180
Worst-case scenario,

362
00:18:20,460 --> 00:18:21,980
Ling Yikai and Zhao Lanxin

363
00:18:22,088 --> 00:18:24,311
have already convinced
employees to resign together.

364
00:18:24,400 --> 00:18:26,555
They planned to leave
after the Chinese New Year,

365
00:18:26,644 --> 00:18:28,577
after collecting their year-end bonuses.

366
00:18:28,780 --> 00:18:29,540
Who knows,

367
00:18:29,700 --> 00:18:30,700
He Han made a sudden move

368
00:18:31,044 --> 00:18:32,422
and exposed things ahead of time?

369
00:18:32,980 --> 00:18:33,540
In theory,

370
00:18:34,660 --> 00:18:35,380
he also helped you

371
00:18:35,380 --> 00:18:36,660
save on year-end bonus expenses.

372
00:18:38,260 --> 00:18:39,420
Please tell Lawyer Bei

373
00:18:40,180 --> 00:18:42,260
that they cannot
take away any of my authors.

374
00:18:44,020 --> 00:18:44,860
Lawyer Bei asks

375
00:18:44,955 --> 00:18:47,577
if there's any chance to
resume cooperation with He Han.

376
00:18:47,620 --> 00:18:48,220
No chance.

377
00:18:50,100 --> 00:18:52,060
Not even a strategic partnership?

378
00:18:52,060 --> 00:18:52,420
No.

379
00:18:58,220 --> 00:18:58,980
Anyone

380
00:18:59,580 --> 00:19:00,460
but He Han.

381
00:19:01,100 --> 00:19:02,050
Without He Han,

382
00:19:02,050 --> 00:19:03,340
the rest don't mean much.

383
00:19:04,380 --> 00:19:05,660
I am Lin Zhanqiao.

384
00:19:06,220 --> 00:19:07,300
He Han is He Han.

385
00:19:08,180 --> 00:19:08,980
If every problem

386
00:19:08,980 --> 00:19:10,260
had the same solution,

387
00:19:10,980 --> 00:19:12,340
why would I go to Lawyer Bei?

388
00:19:12,420 --> 00:19:13,288
Don't you think?

389
00:19:20,780 --> 00:19:21,340
Sorry,

390
00:19:21,500 --> 00:19:23,200
I have an urgent matter to attend to.

391
00:19:25,140 --> 00:19:25,900
What happened?

392
00:19:26,333 --> 00:19:28,044
A friend of mine
was suddenly hospitalized.

393
00:19:28,140 --> 00:19:30,022
By the way,
she's also a client of your firm.

394
00:19:30,377 --> 00:19:31,300
I'll give you a ride.

395
00:19:31,700 --> 00:19:32,380
Thank you.

396
00:19:39,111 --> 00:19:40,511
Hello, may I ask where Zhou Mei is?

397
00:19:40,580 --> 00:19:41,220
I'm her friend.

398
00:19:41,700 --> 00:19:42,180
Over there.

399
00:19:42,620 --> 00:19:43,140
Thank you.

400
00:19:43,260 --> 00:19:44,066
You're welcome.

401
00:19:46,180 --> 00:19:47,540
How is she? Is it serious?

402
00:19:47,700 --> 00:19:49,060
She was pushed down the stairs.

403
00:19:49,300 --> 00:19:51,020
She has multiple soft tissue injuries

404
00:19:51,140 --> 00:19:52,377
and scratches on her face.

405
00:19:52,644 --> 00:19:54,333
These are her medical records and scans.

406
00:19:54,444 --> 00:19:55,220
Please keep them.

407
00:19:55,220 --> 00:19:55,933
Alright, thank you.

408
00:19:57,311 --> 00:19:58,888
Are you trying to get yourself killed?

409
00:19:59,180 --> 00:19:59,980
This kind of thing

410
00:19:59,980 --> 00:20:01,066
can cost a life, you know?

411
00:20:01,088 --> 00:20:03,000
How many lives do you have
to mess around like this?

412
00:20:03,340 --> 00:20:04,180
Who pushed you down?

413
00:20:04,444 --> 00:20:05,666
Was it Li Weifeng's wife?

414
00:20:05,820 --> 00:20:06,620
Not his wife.

415
00:20:07,260 --> 00:20:07,980
It was Li Weifeng.

416
00:20:09,380 --> 00:20:10,340
After I met his wife,

417
00:20:10,340 --> 00:20:11,420
I made things clear to him.

418
00:20:11,430 --> 00:20:12,490
I told him I have a boyfriend

419
00:20:12,500 --> 00:20:14,022
and that we should keep our distance.

420
00:20:14,220 --> 00:20:15,740
But he got very emotional

421
00:20:16,060 --> 00:20:17,140
and started pulling at me.

422
00:20:17,140 --> 00:20:19,460
Why did you show
our chat records to my wife?

423
00:20:21,180 --> 00:20:21,700
Zhou Mei!

424
00:20:21,844 --> 00:20:23,088
He accidentally pushed me down.

425
00:20:23,130 --> 00:20:24,620
Are you out of your mind?

426
00:20:25,300 --> 00:20:26,540
It had nothing to do with you,

427
00:20:26,540 --> 00:20:27,930
yet you insisted on saving
someone else's marriage

428
00:20:27,940 --> 00:20:29,250
and trying to "wake up" his wife?

429
00:20:29,260 --> 00:20:30,866
Look at what you've done to yourself!

430
00:20:30,900 --> 00:20:32,577
You're practically
getting yourself killed!

431
00:20:32,600 --> 00:20:33,860
When people like him lose control,

432
00:20:33,860 --> 00:20:35,140
they just need to vent it out.

433
00:20:35,300 --> 00:20:36,220
I know how this goes.

434
00:20:36,300 --> 00:20:37,020
Don't worry.

435
00:20:37,860 --> 00:20:39,500
Miss Zhou, do you need me? I'm a lawyer.

436
00:20:39,955 --> 00:20:41,620
She's reckless.
Stay out of her business.

437
00:20:41,740 --> 00:20:42,555
Heed my advice.

438
00:20:42,666 --> 00:20:44,733
Keep an eye on her.
If anything happens, call a nurse.

439
00:20:44,777 --> 00:20:45,733
I'll go get the medicine.

440
00:20:46,933 --> 00:20:48,955
If this happens again,
I won't come save you!

441
00:20:49,740 --> 00:20:50,620
One less troublemaker.

442
00:21:18,100 --> 00:21:19,260
Don't look at me like that.

443
00:21:20,180 --> 00:21:20,980
You're not my type.

444
00:21:30,820 --> 00:21:32,220
How are her injuries, Sir?

445
00:21:34,860 --> 00:21:36,220
Zhou Mei's condition

446
00:21:37,060 --> 00:21:38,220
is generally not serious.

447
00:21:38,620 --> 00:21:40,733
The injuries on her face
are only minor scratches.

448
00:21:41,700 --> 00:21:43,100
Most people in this situation

449
00:21:43,100 --> 00:21:44,111
won't be left with scars.

450
00:21:44,155 --> 00:21:45,660
But with certain skin types

451
00:21:45,820 --> 00:21:47,140
or unstable skin conditions,

452
00:21:47,200 --> 00:21:48,577
there might be some issues.

453
00:21:48,755 --> 00:21:50,333
But there can't be any chance of that.

454
00:21:50,500 --> 00:21:52,740
You can consider some
related treatment options.

455
00:21:53,100 --> 00:21:55,020
But these procedures
are not covered by insurance.

456
00:21:55,500 --> 00:21:56,020
That's fine.

457
00:21:56,180 --> 00:21:56,955
Let's do it.

458
00:22:02,540 --> 00:22:03,140
Careful.

459
00:22:13,620 --> 00:22:14,140
Careful.

460
00:22:19,700 --> 00:22:20,180
Inside.

461
00:22:22,340 --> 00:22:22,660
Here.

462
00:22:23,540 --> 00:22:23,940
Alright.

463
00:22:26,780 --> 00:22:27,580
Thank you.

464
00:22:27,700 --> 00:22:28,260
Careful.

465
00:22:31,180 --> 00:22:32,380
Actually, my leg is fine.

466
00:22:32,533 --> 00:22:33,860
The main injuries are on my hand.

467
00:22:35,140 --> 00:22:36,220
And your face.

468
00:22:36,900 --> 00:22:38,020
Just some scratches.

469
00:22:38,933 --> 00:22:41,044
Maybe skip
the cosmetic treatment. It's expensive.

470
00:22:41,660 --> 00:22:42,740
I've already paid.

471
00:22:42,740 --> 00:22:43,700
You have to go.

472
00:22:43,700 --> 00:22:45,022
Just think of it as skincare.

473
00:22:47,622 --> 00:22:48,977
Why are you still here?

474
00:22:50,688 --> 00:22:51,740
I have already written down

475
00:22:51,900 --> 00:22:53,130
the doctor's instructions for

476
00:22:53,130 --> 00:22:54,100
when and how to apply the medicine,

477
00:22:54,100 --> 00:22:55,377
as well as your next
follow-up appointment.

478
00:22:55,580 --> 00:22:56,060
Thank you.

479
00:22:57,177 --> 00:22:58,044
By the way,

480
00:22:58,177 --> 00:23:00,377
I have an appointment
with Lawyer Bei tomorrow at 9 AM.

481
00:23:00,380 --> 00:23:01,511
Can you come pick me up?

482
00:23:01,577 --> 00:23:02,177
Sure.

483
00:23:03,060 --> 00:23:04,650
You're already like this, and you still

484
00:23:04,660 --> 00:23:05,700
want to see Lawyer Bei?

485
00:23:06,500 --> 00:23:07,540
It's just a minor injury.

486
00:23:07,660 --> 00:23:08,580
It won't affect work.

487
00:23:09,100 --> 00:23:09,820
I'm leaving.

488
00:23:09,900 --> 00:23:11,222
You two get some rest.

489
00:23:15,780 --> 00:23:16,740
Thank you for today.

490
00:23:18,820 --> 00:23:19,180
Goodbye.

491
00:23:28,700 --> 00:23:29,580
Who's your boyfriend?

492
00:23:33,380 --> 00:23:34,140
I made it up.

493
00:23:35,300 --> 00:23:36,220
Isn't it Lawyer Bei?

494
00:23:37,340 --> 00:23:38,100
No.

495
00:23:38,844 --> 00:23:41,200
If you don't believe me,
I can show you the chat records.

496
00:23:41,420 --> 00:23:43,333
I don't even have
a situationship right now.

497
00:23:43,444 --> 00:23:45,022
I've been single for a year and a half.

498
00:23:45,300 --> 00:23:46,860
It's not like no one wants you.

499
00:23:47,820 --> 00:23:49,420
There are plenty of eligible single men,

500
00:23:49,420 --> 00:23:50,140
and they're all good.

501
00:23:50,140 --> 00:23:51,555
You don't consider any of them,

502
00:23:51,620 --> 00:23:53,666
yet you insist on getting
involved with married men.

503
00:23:54,260 --> 00:23:56,380
It was well-intentioned
but had a bad outcome.

504
00:23:56,577 --> 00:23:58,066
Can't you show me a little sympathy?

505
00:23:58,900 --> 00:23:59,980
I'm afraid one day

506
00:23:59,980 --> 00:24:01,911
I'll get pushed down
the stairs with you.

507
00:24:01,980 --> 00:24:03,300
That won't happen. Don't worry.

508
00:24:04,740 --> 00:24:06,540
Tomorrow, once I see Lawyer Bei,

509
00:24:06,620 --> 00:24:08,755
I'll help you deal with
Zhao Lanxin and Ling Yikai.

510
00:24:08,940 --> 00:24:09,940
Save it.

511
00:24:11,260 --> 00:24:12,688
What did Zhao Lanxin say to you?

512
00:24:14,220 --> 00:24:14,980
Nothing at all.

513
00:24:16,420 --> 00:24:17,860
Up until now,

514
00:24:18,420 --> 00:24:19,780
she hasn't said a single word.

515
00:24:20,940 --> 00:24:21,540
So now,

516
00:24:22,900 --> 00:24:24,060
everything is being handled

517
00:24:24,820 --> 00:24:26,780
by the Human Resources Department.

518
00:24:27,900 --> 00:24:30,260
You don't criticize her
for abandoning loyalty over looks,

519
00:24:30,580 --> 00:24:32,060
yet you're so harsh on me.

520
00:24:33,540 --> 00:24:34,660
You're my close friend.

521
00:24:35,180 --> 00:24:35,780
But she

522
00:24:36,300 --> 00:24:37,420
is just my business partner,

523
00:24:37,580 --> 00:24:39,140
at most a former schoolmate.

524
00:24:44,980 --> 00:24:46,022
He Han has updated.

525
00:24:48,777 --> 00:24:51,111
(Please select your tip amount.)
Give him 200 yuan.

526
00:24:51,977 --> 00:24:53,866
His copyrights sold
for tens of millions.

527
00:24:53,888 --> 00:24:56,340
Your tip isn't even
enough to make a dent.

528
00:24:57,100 --> 00:24:58,300
You might as well save it

529
00:24:58,300 --> 00:25:00,240
and tip new authors instead,
to encourage them.

530
00:25:00,340 --> 00:25:02,111
There are so many
online fiction authors.

531
00:25:02,340 --> 00:25:04,311
Survival of the fittest
has always been the rule.

532
00:25:04,580 --> 00:25:06,755
I don't have any obligation
to encourage newcomers.

533
00:25:07,100 --> 00:25:08,260
What they need is skill,

534
00:25:08,500 --> 00:25:09,260
not handouts.

535
00:25:09,460 --> 00:25:10,733
I've put your medicine here.

536
00:25:10,777 --> 00:25:12,911
Call me if you need anything.
Get some rest. Good night.

537
00:25:13,100 --> 00:25:14,733
Rushing back to read the update?

538
00:25:15,340 --> 00:25:15,820
No time.

539
00:25:28,933 --> 00:25:31,300
It's not easy to get you out for dinner.

540
00:25:31,622 --> 00:25:34,000
But there should be plenty
more chances from now on.

541
00:25:46,340 --> 00:25:47,660
I'll be patient with you.

542
00:25:48,660 --> 00:25:49,980
You'll come around, Ling Yikai.

543
00:25:55,180 --> 00:25:55,860
Kiss me.

544
00:26:01,580 --> 00:26:02,940
You said you have patience.

545
00:26:03,311 --> 00:26:04,711
Can't you wait a little longer?

546
00:26:04,820 --> 00:26:06,100
Since this is a partnership,

547
00:26:06,100 --> 00:26:07,580
I've already shown my sincerity.

548
00:26:08,220 --> 00:26:09,380
You should show some too.

549
00:26:09,777 --> 00:26:11,555
Otherwise, where do we even begin?

550
00:26:24,860 --> 00:26:25,660
I meant here.

551
00:26:54,666 --> 00:26:55,711
That's enough, right?

552
00:26:59,140 --> 00:27:00,340
You need me, Ling Yikai,

553
00:27:01,540 --> 00:27:02,660
more than I need you.

554
00:27:05,140 --> 00:27:06,340
Let's go. Take me home.

555
00:27:51,260 --> 00:27:52,260
Zhanqiao, look.

556
00:27:52,460 --> 00:27:53,933
Written by He Han's girlfriend.

557
00:27:55,300 --> 00:27:56,020
I saw it.

558
00:28:00,900 --> 00:28:03,460
♪I keep asking myself♪

559
00:28:05,340 --> 00:28:08,820
♪What it is I should become♪

560
00:28:17,220 --> 00:28:20,860
(Rating: 1 star)

561
00:28:28,140 --> 00:28:31,220
♪Like a drifting dandelion♪

562
00:28:32,820 --> 00:28:36,020
♪Turning where it drifts♪

563
00:28:36,780 --> 00:28:41,860
♪Into soil where it can grow♪

564
00:28:43,700 --> 00:28:46,700
♪When the rain comes, I hide♪

565
00:28:47,580 --> 00:28:50,580
♪In a flower shop at the corner♪

566
00:28:51,140 --> 00:28:57,060
♪Even spring borrows its fragrance♪

567
00:29:58,622 --> 00:29:59,600
Good morning, Ms. Lin.

568
00:29:59,740 --> 00:30:00,100
Morning.

569
00:30:13,420 --> 00:30:18,060
(Resignation Letter)

570
00:30:23,780 --> 00:30:28,020
(Resignation Letter)

571
00:30:34,740 --> 00:30:35,180
Bo.

572
00:30:38,800 --> 00:30:39,822
Call a meeting now

573
00:30:39,888 --> 00:30:42,222
for all editors who haven't
submitted resignation letters.

574
00:30:44,060 --> 00:30:45,660
I submitted mine, too.

575
00:30:49,180 --> 00:30:49,660
Why?

576
00:30:50,060 --> 00:30:51,940
Mr. Zhao said he
wants me to be an editor.

577
00:30:55,460 --> 00:30:56,666
You want to be an editor?

578
00:30:58,260 --> 00:30:59,420
I mentioned it to you before.

579
00:30:59,860 --> 00:31:00,977
You may have forgotten.

580
00:31:01,180 --> 00:31:02,800
You don't really pay attention to us.

581
00:31:03,020 --> 00:31:04,500
Maybe you've been too busy with work.

582
00:31:06,740 --> 00:31:07,220
I'm sorry.

583
00:31:07,500 --> 00:31:08,711
I really don't remember.

584
00:31:09,940 --> 00:31:10,900
But your resignation

585
00:31:10,900 --> 00:31:11,940
hasn't been approved yet.

586
00:31:12,340 --> 00:31:13,580
You're still my assistant.

587
00:31:14,020 --> 00:31:14,820
Do as I say.

588
00:31:36,260 --> 00:31:36,860
Nine.

589
00:31:38,020 --> 00:31:38,940
Better than I expected.

590
00:31:39,220 --> 00:31:40,380
Including me, that makes ten.

591
00:31:40,940 --> 00:31:41,660
Not too few.

592
00:31:42,700 --> 00:31:43,688
Take a look at this.

593
00:31:45,060 --> 00:31:45,980
Right now,

594
00:31:45,980 --> 00:31:47,660
we have over 300 new authors.

595
00:31:48,060 --> 00:31:49,220
With ten editors,

596
00:31:49,220 --> 00:31:50,820
that means each person

597
00:31:50,820 --> 00:31:52,177
is responsible for 34 authors.

598
00:31:52,266 --> 00:31:53,866
That's basically impossible.

599
00:31:54,111 --> 00:31:55,340
We're already in the process

600
00:31:55,340 --> 00:31:56,622
of recruiting new editors,

601
00:31:56,980 --> 00:31:58,020
but it will take some time.

602
00:31:58,700 --> 00:31:59,860
My current plan

603
00:32:00,377 --> 00:32:02,311
is to drop some of
the lower-tier authors.

604
00:32:03,222 --> 00:32:05,266
Some of them started
with us from the beginning.

605
00:32:05,311 --> 00:32:07,410
If they don't have what it takes,
they have to go.

606
00:32:07,422 --> 00:32:09,060
Many of those who left today

607
00:32:09,140 --> 00:32:11,088
also joined us
right after graduation, right?

608
00:32:13,860 --> 00:32:14,340
Ms. Lin,

609
00:32:14,622 --> 00:32:16,755
cutting the lower-tier authors
isn't the solution.

610
00:32:16,940 --> 00:32:19,010
First, some authors have potential.

611
00:32:19,010 --> 00:32:20,060
They're still on the rise.

612
00:32:20,380 --> 00:32:21,140
Cutting them

613
00:32:21,140 --> 00:32:22,620
means cutting off future growth.

614
00:32:22,780 --> 00:32:23,140
Second,

615
00:32:23,460 --> 00:32:24,020
top authors

616
00:32:24,020 --> 00:32:25,555
require more of our time and effort.

617
00:32:25,580 --> 00:32:27,700
Right now, even one editor
handling two top authors

618
00:32:27,940 --> 00:32:29,140
is already stretched.

619
00:32:29,140 --> 00:32:30,700
In that case,

620
00:32:31,022 --> 00:32:32,222
with the nine of us,

621
00:32:32,340 --> 00:32:34,220
we can keep at most around 20 authors.

622
00:32:34,377 --> 00:32:35,622
I'll make the selection.

623
00:32:37,180 --> 00:32:38,380
The authors we have

624
00:32:38,380 --> 00:32:40,400
have different levels
of connection with us.

625
00:32:40,740 --> 00:32:42,580
You can't just
terminate contracts like that.

626
00:32:42,844 --> 00:32:44,511
We have to weigh the pros and cons.

627
00:32:44,700 --> 00:32:46,860
If it affects
our reputation in the industry,

628
00:32:47,222 --> 00:32:49,466
it'll be hard to work
with them again in the future.

629
00:32:55,220 --> 00:32:56,100
Let results speak.

630
00:32:58,740 --> 00:32:59,820
Not relationships.

631
00:33:01,260 --> 00:33:03,020
If we're still relying
on personal ties now,

632
00:33:03,466 --> 00:33:05,100
it will only get harder going forward.

633
00:33:05,460 --> 00:33:06,900
But we're all sitting here today

634
00:33:07,540 --> 00:33:08,860
because we considered those ties.

635
00:33:18,380 --> 00:33:19,500
Thank you, everyone.

636
00:33:19,888 --> 00:33:22,111
I'll start by making a list
based on hard metrics.

637
00:33:22,300 --> 00:33:23,540
If there are any further issues,

638
00:33:23,933 --> 00:33:25,511
I'll handle them individually.

639
00:33:48,940 --> 00:33:49,620
The water's full.

640
00:33:53,422 --> 00:33:55,090
Came up here just to see me
make a fool of myself?

641
00:33:55,100 --> 00:33:56,660
Come on, I just passed by.

642
00:33:57,420 --> 00:33:58,740
You don't look too good.

643
00:33:59,820 --> 00:34:02,140
Who is number one on your side now,
besides Hong Qigong?

644
00:34:02,150 --> 00:34:03,730
And she's surely
signing with Zhao Lanxin.

645
00:34:03,740 --> 00:34:04,933
I won't believe it again.

646
00:34:07,020 --> 00:34:08,100
It's real this time.

647
00:34:09,140 --> 00:34:10,660
Lin Zhanqiao, think of something.

648
00:34:10,880 --> 00:34:13,266
Other than Hong Qigong, you
don't have anyone who can compete.

649
00:34:13,340 --> 00:34:14,140
If this keeps up,

650
00:34:14,140 --> 00:34:16,155
you won't even catch up to me barefoot.

651
00:34:25,620 --> 00:34:26,622
So you've given up?

652
00:34:27,820 --> 00:34:28,140
Fine.

653
00:34:29,180 --> 00:34:30,860
I like seeing that look on your face,

654
00:34:30,940 --> 00:34:32,533
gritting your teeth as you lose to me.

655
00:34:33,111 --> 00:34:34,822
Don't forget to check my update tonight.

656
00:34:43,777 --> 00:34:46,266
Hong Qigong is negotiating
a contract with Zhao Lanxin.

657
00:35:04,540 --> 00:35:05,460
Did you come here

658
00:35:05,460 --> 00:35:06,460
just to tell me that?

659
00:35:07,940 --> 00:35:08,500
What else?

660
00:35:08,888 --> 00:35:09,888
I care about you.

661
00:35:36,977 --> 00:35:38,300
Mr. Ling, take a look at this.

662
00:35:39,060 --> 00:35:39,460
Ms. Lin.

663
00:35:40,333 --> 00:35:41,490
Does this need to be revised?

664
00:35:42,100 --> 00:35:43,020
Who signed this before?

665
00:35:44,100 --> 00:35:44,540
Ms. Lin.

666
00:35:46,500 --> 00:35:46,820
Alright.

667
00:35:47,700 --> 00:35:48,380
No issues.

668
00:35:49,220 --> 00:35:50,020
What about this one?

669
00:35:50,540 --> 00:35:51,600
Where is Zhao Lanxin?

670
00:35:53,400 --> 00:35:54,820
She's already completed her handover.

671
00:35:54,820 --> 00:35:56,222
She's taken a few days of sick leave.

672
00:35:56,300 --> 00:35:57,511
Is she avoiding me on purpose?

673
00:35:57,700 --> 00:35:58,780
It would be awkward to meet.

674
00:35:59,260 --> 00:36:00,420
She poached Hong Qigong?

675
00:36:00,620 --> 00:36:02,288
I still don't know how their talks went.

676
00:36:02,660 --> 00:36:03,500
When are you leaving?

677
00:36:04,300 --> 00:36:06,990
Tomorrow. Equity transfer has been
completed according to the procedures.

678
00:36:07,060 --> 00:36:08,244
Have you completed the handover

679
00:36:08,250 --> 00:36:09,850
for Zhiyuan Investment's
connections and progress?

680
00:36:09,860 --> 00:36:10,380
No need.

681
00:36:10,660 --> 00:36:12,444
Their funding won't go
to Chenxing anymore.

682
00:36:12,666 --> 00:36:14,688
I'll be taking both
the money and the connections.

683
00:36:14,780 --> 00:36:17,333
Otherwise, how do you think
I could start a company outside?

684
00:36:19,100 --> 00:36:20,500
Chenxing's past business foundation

685
00:36:20,860 --> 00:36:22,300
isn't something your startup

686
00:36:22,300 --> 00:36:23,060
can compare to.

687
00:36:23,220 --> 00:36:24,622
You said it yourself, it's the past.

688
00:36:24,660 --> 00:36:27,311
Even married couples go
their separate ways in tough times,

689
00:36:27,422 --> 00:36:29,488
let alone colleagues.

690
00:36:30,580 --> 00:36:32,580
Investors look
at the future, not the past.

691
00:36:33,260 --> 00:36:34,311
Let me put it this way.

692
00:36:35,180 --> 00:36:35,700
He Han

693
00:36:35,940 --> 00:36:38,500
is Chenxing's past, present, and future.

694
00:36:38,700 --> 00:36:39,820
I'm sorry, but you're not.

695
00:36:40,020 --> 00:36:41,244
When I run a company,

696
00:36:41,500 --> 00:36:43,580
a strong author isn't just He Han.

697
00:36:44,022 --> 00:36:46,000
And the market
doesn't rely on just one author.

698
00:36:46,066 --> 00:36:46,955
Do you have one now?

699
00:36:48,220 --> 00:36:49,020
If not,

700
00:36:49,220 --> 00:36:51,533
you need to give everyone
in the company, including me,

701
00:36:52,380 --> 00:36:53,660
a reason to keep betting on you.

702
00:36:56,533 --> 00:36:58,466
Anyone who leaves without consulting me

703
00:36:58,800 --> 00:37:00,533
doesn't deserve to hear my reasons.

704
00:37:00,820 --> 00:37:01,700
And Ling Yikai,

705
00:37:02,780 --> 00:37:03,500
don't really think

706
00:37:03,500 --> 00:37:04,980
you can control Zhao Lanxin.

707
00:37:05,333 --> 00:37:07,022
I've worked with her for seven years.

708
00:37:07,460 --> 00:37:08,740
We knew each other in university.

709
00:37:09,355 --> 00:37:11,422
Zhou Mei was her
classmate for four years.

710
00:37:12,133 --> 00:37:13,688
I know her better than you.

711
00:37:53,180 --> 00:37:54,540
I'm with Zhao Lanxin right now.

712
00:37:54,933 --> 00:37:56,888
Do you want to join us
for a schoolmate lunch?

713
00:38:00,533 --> 00:38:02,177
I was planning to ask you out

714
00:38:02,180 --> 00:38:03,511
after I officially leave Chenxing.

715
00:38:04,340 --> 00:38:05,420
It's for personal reasons

716
00:38:05,420 --> 00:38:07,044
that I've decided to leave Chenxing

717
00:38:07,088 --> 00:38:08,500
and start a business with Ling Yikai.

718
00:38:08,580 --> 00:38:10,155
It's not convenient
to say at the company.

719
00:38:11,940 --> 00:38:13,340
Did Ling Yikai make you feel

720
00:38:13,540 --> 00:38:15,377
like you had a chance
to be his girlfriend?

721
00:38:15,660 --> 00:38:16,060
Yes.

722
00:38:16,600 --> 00:38:17,688
And you believed that?

723
00:38:20,260 --> 00:38:21,780
Everyone knows I like Ling Yikai.

724
00:38:22,860 --> 00:38:23,900
My conditions aren't great.

725
00:38:24,244 --> 00:38:25,200
Not compared to you.

726
00:38:26,860 --> 00:38:28,060
Zhou Mei, you're his ex.

727
00:38:28,660 --> 00:38:30,100
He could live or die for you,

728
00:38:30,740 --> 00:38:31,740
yet you still dumped him.

729
00:38:32,266 --> 00:38:34,644
Lin Zhanqiao, you have
influence in the industry.

730
00:38:34,780 --> 00:38:35,888
You made He Han famous.

731
00:38:36,060 --> 00:38:36,860
He doesn't like you,

732
00:38:37,740 --> 00:38:39,311
but he could still show you affection

733
00:38:39,420 --> 00:38:40,533
and even propose to you.

734
00:38:43,060 --> 00:38:44,140
He's capable of that.

735
00:38:45,380 --> 00:38:46,500
But what if you said yes?

736
00:38:47,888 --> 00:38:48,820
I'm not like you two.

737
00:38:49,066 --> 00:38:50,377
So I don't have that chance.

738
00:38:51,044 --> 00:38:52,733
What's so great about Ling Yikai

739
00:38:53,044 --> 00:38:54,533
that makes you feel he's the one?

740
00:38:59,740 --> 00:39:00,820
People always aim higher.

741
00:39:01,380 --> 00:39:02,580
If I'm getting married, I'll

742
00:39:02,580 --> 00:39:04,488
choose someone
with better conditions than I have.

743
00:39:04,700 --> 00:39:06,911
The ones with better
conditions are hard to handle.

744
00:39:07,155 --> 00:39:09,466
Whether it's Ling Yikai or anyone else,
it's the same.

745
00:39:10,060 --> 00:39:11,460
The ones too good, I can't reach.

746
00:39:12,220 --> 00:39:13,500
The ones not so good

747
00:39:13,888 --> 00:39:15,977
are often more
calculating in my experience.

748
00:39:16,177 --> 00:39:17,933
I don't need to suffer on both sides.

749
00:39:18,860 --> 00:39:20,500
Among the men I can reach,

750
00:39:20,520 --> 00:39:22,200
Ling Yikai has
the best overall conditions.

751
00:39:23,288 --> 00:39:24,733
He has one more advantage.

752
00:39:25,500 --> 00:39:27,140
He doesn't hide his ambition.

753
00:39:27,177 --> 00:39:29,400
Everything, good or bad,
is laid out in the open.

754
00:39:30,022 --> 00:39:32,288
In that sense, he's better
than many hypocrites.

755
00:39:33,044 --> 00:39:34,733
No matter how good the conditions are,

756
00:39:35,500 --> 00:39:36,460
if he doesn't like you,

757
00:39:38,000 --> 00:39:40,133
isn't it just marrying
for the sake of marriage?

758
00:39:43,422 --> 00:39:45,060
How many people actually marry for love?

759
00:39:45,511 --> 00:39:47,733
And even if they do,
does it guarantee happiness?

760
00:39:49,180 --> 00:39:50,300
Marriage is meant

761
00:39:50,300 --> 00:39:51,540
to improve the quality of life.

762
00:39:58,540 --> 00:39:59,340
You're my friend.

763
00:40:00,340 --> 00:40:01,740
I know this isn't very loyal,

764
00:40:02,133 --> 00:40:03,420
but the opportunity is rare.

765
00:40:04,020 --> 00:40:04,740
I want to try.

766
00:40:07,300 --> 00:40:08,111
I understand.

767
00:40:09,022 --> 00:40:10,540
But we're not really friends anymore.

768
00:40:11,980 --> 00:40:14,180
Once he stabilizes
and finds new support,

769
00:40:14,460 --> 00:40:15,460
he'll drop you.

770
00:40:18,020 --> 00:40:19,580
It'll depend on my own ability.

771
00:40:20,420 --> 00:40:21,380
Why put yourself

772
00:40:21,380 --> 00:40:22,180
in such a passive

773
00:40:22,180 --> 00:40:23,580
and exhausting situation?

774
00:40:24,260 --> 00:40:25,220
Aren't you the same?

775
00:40:25,555 --> 00:40:27,422
Going after married men again and again.

776
00:40:27,700 --> 00:40:29,340
Aren't you passive?
Aren't you exhausted?

777
00:40:30,111 --> 00:40:31,220
When people talk about you,

778
00:40:31,220 --> 00:40:33,220
it's probably harsher
than what you say about me.

779
00:40:33,740 --> 00:40:35,688
But everyone has
their own reasons, right?

780
00:40:36,860 --> 00:40:37,900
Zhanqiao, aren't you tired?

781
00:40:38,660 --> 00:40:40,260
All these years, working for He Han.

782
00:40:40,540 --> 00:40:41,860
He earns millions in royalties.

783
00:40:41,977 --> 00:40:44,180
Aside from what you're owed,
what has he given you?

784
00:40:44,580 --> 00:40:45,860
He wouldn't even spare

785
00:40:45,860 --> 00:40:47,220
a place for your toothbrush.

786
00:40:48,488 --> 00:40:50,111
Only half a month after breaking up,

787
00:40:50,200 --> 00:40:51,300
he's already out in public

788
00:40:51,300 --> 00:40:53,420
with whatever new girlfriend he has.

789
00:40:54,333 --> 00:40:55,540
When you were together,

790
00:40:55,540 --> 00:40:56,540
there was love, right?

791
00:40:57,420 --> 00:40:58,460
Yet it ended up even worse.

792
00:41:01,244 --> 00:41:02,644
Excuse me, the bill, please.

793
00:41:02,860 --> 00:41:03,580
Yes, one moment.

794
00:41:03,977 --> 00:41:04,770
Let's split it.

795
00:41:04,770 --> 00:41:07,377
I don't think we'll have another chance
to sit down for a meal again.

796
00:41:08,060 --> 00:41:09,860
How did you convince Hong Qigong

797
00:41:09,860 --> 00:41:11,020
to sign with you?

798
00:41:12,060 --> 00:41:14,140
For someone like her,

799
00:41:14,755 --> 00:41:16,577
a new company isn't the best choice.

800
00:41:18,820 --> 00:41:19,820
We offered more money.

801
00:41:20,780 --> 00:41:22,300
Everything else is just an excuse.

802
00:41:23,355 --> 00:41:25,420
She always thought
the previous offer was too low.

803
00:41:25,911 --> 00:41:26,977
This contract price

804
00:41:27,180 --> 00:41:28,460
was only finalized today.

805
00:41:40,860 --> 00:41:41,820
So Hong Qigong

806
00:41:41,820 --> 00:41:43,740
showed you
what "life is like a show" is.

807
00:41:43,822 --> 00:41:45,622
She made sure
she wouldn't lose either way.

808
00:41:45,688 --> 00:41:47,422
Now that she's signed with Zhao Lanxin,

809
00:41:47,540 --> 00:41:49,700
she can say she left
because you didn't trust her.

810
00:41:50,460 --> 00:41:52,100
If Zhao Lanxin doesn't pay enough,

811
00:41:52,260 --> 00:41:54,140
she can turn around and say
she's loyal to you.

812
00:41:55,420 --> 00:41:56,740
So He Han wasn't wrong.

813
00:42:04,660 --> 00:42:07,380
(Funding Allocation Plan,
Chenxing Culture Media Co., Ltd.)

814
00:42:09,180 --> 00:42:09,700
Done?

815
00:42:11,340 --> 00:42:12,500
Ling Yikai intercepted it.

816
00:42:14,100 --> 00:42:15,100
So once he leaves,

817
00:42:15,180 --> 00:42:18,000
the company's investment side
will be left without leadership.

818
00:42:18,260 --> 00:42:19,740
That's why I had to ask for your help.

819
00:42:20,460 --> 00:42:23,900
I'm ashamed
I ever dated someone like that.

820
00:42:24,044 --> 00:42:25,822
Haven't you dated enough jerks already?

821
00:42:28,420 --> 00:42:29,940
Check the time. What's going on?

822
00:42:29,940 --> 00:42:30,620
It's 3:10 PM.

823
00:42:31,333 --> 00:42:32,100
Good day, Ms. Lin.

824
00:42:32,222 --> 00:42:33,180
Updates stopped.

825
00:42:33,740 --> 00:42:34,180
Ms. Lin.

826
00:42:34,888 --> 00:42:35,940
What are you looking at?

827
00:42:36,000 --> 00:42:38,219
He Han's Shattered Six States
will be paused for a week.

828
00:42:38,220 --> 00:42:39,111
It was just posted.

829
00:42:40,755 --> 00:42:42,977
Ms. Lin, Shattered Six States
is pausing for a week.

830
00:42:43,020 --> 00:42:44,666
Ms. Lin, He Han has stopped updating.

831
00:42:51,820 --> 00:42:52,740
Hello!

832
00:42:53,020 --> 00:42:54,420
Today, I have

833
00:42:54,420 --> 00:42:55,933
a very important announcement.

834
00:42:56,340 --> 00:42:57,300
Starting today,

835
00:42:57,780 --> 00:42:59,780
Shattered Six States
will be paused for a week.

836
00:43:05,780 --> 00:43:07,300
This is Lin Zhanqiao. Meet your new boss.

837
00:43:07,460 --> 00:43:09,140
I'm a big fan of Mr. He Han.

838
00:43:09,620 --> 00:43:11,060
Don't say I'm not being a good sport.

839
00:43:11,580 --> 00:43:13,020
I'll give you one week

840
00:43:13,020 --> 00:43:14,420
to find a better author.

841
00:43:14,460 --> 00:43:15,220
If you're so capable,

842
00:43:15,460 --> 00:43:16,860
try stopping updates for a month.

843
00:43:17,580 --> 00:43:19,260
Let's see
if you're still invincible then.

844
00:43:21,460 --> 00:43:22,100
Didn't you say

845
00:43:22,100 --> 00:43:23,420
you weren't going to see her anymore?

846
00:43:23,820 --> 00:43:24,860
We are truly in love.

847
00:43:25,060 --> 00:43:25,820
Please show some mercy.

848
00:43:26,060 --> 00:43:27,940
You're "truly in love"
when he has money,

849
00:43:28,420 --> 00:43:30,060
but when he's broke,
the "spark is gone."

850
00:43:30,580 --> 00:43:32,180
Even streetwalkers
have more shame than you.

851
00:43:35,460 --> 00:43:36,020
What are you doing?

852
00:43:36,020 --> 00:43:36,420
You...

853
00:43:39,161 --> 00:43:40,281
(I've been thinking.)

854
00:43:41,561 --> 00:43:44,841
(Everyone's most comfortable level of intimacy)

855
00:43:45,601 --> 00:43:52,931
(is probably different.)

856
00:43:53,931 --> 00:43:55,681
♪If the sky♪

857
00:43:56,191 --> 00:43:57,591
♪And the sea♪

858
00:43:58,131 --> 00:43:59,841
♪Turned upside down♪

859
00:44:01,401 --> 00:44:03,331
♪If a swimming fish♪

860
00:44:03,731 --> 00:44:07,121
♪Fell in love with a flying bird♪

861
00:44:08,891 --> 00:44:10,861
♪If back then♪

862
00:44:11,221 --> 00:44:15,631
♪We had never let go♪

863
00:44:16,231 --> 00:44:22,511
♪We wouldn't be lost in the crowd♪

864
00:44:23,631 --> 00:44:25,781
♪We met in a thirteenth month♪

865
00:44:25,781 --> 00:44:27,651
♪Held each other in a fifth season♪

866
00:44:27,831 --> 00:44:30,271
♪And found our way back whole♪

867
00:44:31,111 --> 00:44:33,281
♪So let this surging love♪

868
00:44:33,281 --> 00:44:37,711
♪Rise like tides that never fall♪

869
00:44:38,611 --> 00:44:40,791
♪If we're caught in a pouring rain♪

870
00:44:40,791 --> 00:44:41,881
♪That's alright♪

871
00:44:42,421 --> 00:44:43,171
♪If we're buried♪

872
00:44:43,171 --> 00:44:45,871
♪By passing years all the better♪

873
00:44:46,131 --> 00:44:48,311
♪At least we still can keep♪

874
00:44:48,491 --> 00:44:52,911
♪This one eternal photograph♪

875
00:45:08,671 --> 00:45:10,961
♪We're on misaligned tracks♪

876
00:45:10,961 --> 00:45:12,721
♪Running in opposite ways♪

877
00:45:12,841 --> 00:45:15,311
♪Searching all along the way♪

878
00:45:16,111 --> 00:45:18,271
♪For the fire of our younger hearts♪

879
00:45:18,461 --> 00:45:23,371
♪And the beauty lost in time♪

880
00:45:23,371 --> 00:45:26,891
♪This time don't lose each other again♪

881
00:45:27,131 --> 00:45:28,101
♪Only after loss♪

882
00:45:28,101 --> 00:45:30,731
♪Do we learn what truly matters most♪

883
00:45:31,141 --> 00:45:33,501
♪In another time and space♪

884
00:45:33,501 --> 00:45:35,061
♪We'll stay and walk together♪

885
00:45:35,061 --> 00:45:37,891
♪Till we grow old♪

886
00:45:38,851 --> 00:45:41,141
♪But still the sky will never♪

887
00:45:41,141 --> 00:45:43,811
♪Turn with the sea♪

888
00:45:46,331 --> 00:45:48,741
♪But still a swimming fish won't♪

889
00:45:48,741 --> 00:45:53,951
♪Fall in love with a flying bird♪
